I should remind everyone one  about the following physical<br>
principles. <br>
1. All momentum in a frictionless enviroment such as the vacume of space is conserved.<br>
2. In an elastic collision the momentum of all <br>
the things that collide must be conserved, and <br>
must be equivelent wnen added together.<br>
3. The collision of the plasma pulse from a nuclear explosion with orions pusher plate is an elastic collision.<br>
4. In physics the momentum that is conserved is eqaul<br>
to the mass of the  matter in motion multiplied by the velocity<br>
of the motion when the collision occurrs.<br>
5.From 1945 to 1993 the debris velocity of all nuclear test explosions was calculated, and measured emperically to verify it by the instuments used to collect physics data from the test when it occured.This data verified yield, spectrum of all nuclear radiations, radius, and velocity of shock wave et el.<br>
6. All of this 48 years of collected measurements, and calculations were used to create the computer models now used for studying nuclear weapon, and explosion physics.<br>
These computer models are of course classified top level top secret by Los Alamos et el for national security reasons.<br>
