the total momentum of the plasma shock wave that hits it.<br>
11. If  I explode a 10 megaton bomb with a debris velocity of 30,000 km/sec and a mass of 5000 kg the total momentum of of its entire mass is :150,000,000,000 kg which is <br>
330,000,000,000 pounds. If the steel plate can take 10,000<br>
