3.14 devided into 33,000,000 is a little over 10,000,000<br>
then devide by 2 . This is 5000,000. Now take the sqaure root of 5,000,000 .This is about 2400  inches at most. Now<br>
devide by 12. This 200 feet. Now devide by 3. This is<br>
about 70 meters in radiaus which is 140, meters in diameter.<br>
Now rember of 10 megaton pus we will use a 34000 meter<br>
diameter plate to achieve 50 % collimation of the plasma pulse.. Now decide how thick a  pusher plate you want.<br>
